tip.text: Flights are $8 + free popcorn/byo GF food. Love their beer! The honey pale ale and coffee dark ale are my favorites

This place is amazing. Try the Lak Sa (noodle soup) and Coco-Cauliflower dish. Warm, savory and just the right amount of spice. Pair with ginger tea or green Thai iced tea.
Taste everything for $7 -- a great deal, and these guys know what they're doing.
Affordable sushi of great quality. Yum!
Our favorites: cebiche "5 elementos", causa mixta nikkei, lomo saltado and quinoa risotto (chisaya mama).
